==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-lawyer.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔɪə(r)|-ɔɪə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[professional]] person authorized to practice [[law]], conduct lawsuits or give legal advice .
# By extension, a person who argues points of law.


